    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-04-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-04-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="1035"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1035">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Polo de Bernabé</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Sherman</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Spain in Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,<lb/>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-04-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 2, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 33.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. Secretary</hi>: I have the honor, by order of my
                    Government, to transmit to your excellency the full testimony<note n="3"
                        xml:id="d1035fn3">The full report is published in Senate Report No. 885,
                        Fifty-fifth Congress, second session.</note> in the inquiry instituted by
                    the maritime authority of the Habana station by reason of the catastrophe which
                    befell the U. S. ironclad <hi rend="italic">Maine</hi> in that port, in <pb
                        facs="1142" n="1046" xml:id="pg_1046"/> the night of the 15th of February
                    last, which awful misfortune to the American people has been so deeply and
                    sincerely lamented by the Spanish Government and people.</p>
                <p>I improve this opportunity, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Louis Polo de Bernabé.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
